id: pm-3pbq
title: "pm history-compact: checkpoint-based history stream compaction"
description: Each mutation appends a JSONL line; long-lived high-activity items grow unboundedly. No checkpoint/snapshot primitive collapses early entries.
type: Feature
status: in_progress
priority: 3
tags[4]: "area:history","area:storage",living-map,performance
created_at: "2026-05-31T19:43:38.117Z"
updated_at: "2026-06-06T16:50:35.918Z"
assignee: codex-agent
author: maintainer-agent
acceptance_criteria: "pm history-compact <id> [--before] [--dry-run] replays to a synthetic baseline entry, removes prior entries, re-anchors chain; passes verifyHistoryChain; restore+history work; rollback on failure."
value: Each mutation appends a JSONL line; long-lived high-activity items grow unboundedly. No checkpoint/snapshot primitive collapses early entries.
parent: pm-o2kc
comments[4]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-06-06T16:21:57.739Z",codex-agent,"Orientation baseline: branch=feat/history-compact-toon-tracking-coverage, repo clean on main before claim, no duplicate open item beyond pm-3pbq for history compaction. GH baseline: open issues=0, open PRs=0, dependabot alerts=0, code-scanning endpoint returns no-analysis for current token scope. CI on main green; recent feature-branch failures traced to deterministic test assertion drift (search-command), not current scope."
  "2026-06-06T16:31:01.313Z",codex-agent,"Implemented history-compact end-to-end: added command runtime (checkpoint boundary parsing, synthetic baseline + retained-tail re-anchoring, verifyHistoryChain gate, dry-run, lock+ownership checks, drift detection, rollback-safe atomic writes, audit marker), wired CLI registration/exports/help/completions/contracts/MCP action routing, regenerated full contracts fixture, and added unit+integration assertions. Focused verification passed: pnpm build; pnpm contracts:update; node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/history-compact-command.spec.ts tests/unit/completion-command.spec.ts tests/unit/contracts-command.spec.ts tests/integration/release-readiness-runtime.spec.ts."
  "2026-06-06T16:46:11.973Z",codex-agent,"Coverage campaign evidence: ran full suite under strict thresholds with node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage (2497 tests, 146 files) and achieved 100% statements/branches/functions/lines for the configured source coverage surface. Also updated release-readiness coverage-alignment assertions to keep intentional curated include behavior explicit and prevent accidental wildcard broadening."
  "2026-06-06T16:50:35.918Z",manual-smoke,"Final verification evidence: full gate suite passed (pnpm build; pnpm typecheck; node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage => 2497 tests + 100% thresholds on configured surface; pnpm contracts:check; pnpm changelog:pm:check; pnpm security:scan; pm validate --check-resolution --check-history-drift; pm health --check-only). Manual packed-install smoke passed in isolated temp dir (/tmp/tmp.PJyjDpTqrN) using npm pack artifact unbrained-pm-cli-2026.6.6.tgz and end-to-end commands create/update/history --verify/history-compact dry-run+apply/restore/history --verify. GitHub baseline re-check: open issues=0, open PRs=0, dependabot open alerts=[]; code-scanning endpoint still reports no analysis + missing admin:repo_hook scope. Dependency/vuln checks: pnpm outdated shows commander 14.0.3 -> 15.0.0 only; pnpm audit reports no known vulnerabilities. Telemetry health verified via pm telemetry status/stats (successful recent flush timestamps and fresh command events). Sentry CLI connectivity verified (auth token org=unbrained, project=pm-cli), but issue-list API is 403 due token permission scope."
